  "note": "Relational questions answered from the typed-edge graph (works_at edges, people.relation, org existence). The scorer resolves each via repo graph primitives (entitiesNamedIn/oneHopNeighbors + relation/org reads) — never the LLM. 'relevant' lists the brain page that documents the relation, so retrieval-side hit@3 is also measured. 'graph' carries the structured probe + expected substrings (sealed).",
